# Dataset Information

## Text Dataset (NLP)
- Custom dataset split into training and testing sets
- Used for text classification tasks
- Automatically processed in notebook using PyTorch Dataset class

## Image Dataset (CIFAR-10)
- Automatically downloaded using torchvision.datasets.CIFAR10
- Contains 10 classes of images:
  airplane, automobile, bird, cat, deer, dog, frog, horse, ship, truck

## Access Notes
- No manual download required
- Datasets are automatically loaded when running the notebook
- CIFAR-10 will be downloaded on first execution
